name: v2.57.0
body:
## What's Changed
* Set window title to "Caprine" by @lefterisgar in https://github.com/sindresorhus/caprine/pull/1889
* Merge css stylesheets by @lefterisgar in https://github.com/sindresorhus/caprine/pull/1891

* Add rpm spec by @dusansimic in https://github.com/sindresorhus/caprine/pull/1896
* Remove new "Install Messenger app" banner by @mquevill in https://github.com/sindresorhus/caprine/pull/1899
* Fix custom css default file by @dusansimic in https://github.com/sindresorhus/caprine/pull/1903
* Fix search close button color in dark mode by @dusansimic in https://github.com/sindresorhus/caprine/pull/1931
* Fix attachment and receiver pill background in dark mode by @sfrunza13 in https://github.com/sindresorhus/caprine/pull/1933
* Fix "Join room" background button on dark theme by @jrafaelsantana in https://github.com/sindresorhus/caprine/pull/1938
* Fix create room icon color in dark mode by @jrafaelsantana in https://github.com/sindresorhus/caprine/pull/1937
* CI: Use setup-node action for caching by @lefterisgar in https://github.com/sindresorhus/caprine/pull/1941
* Fix dark mode icons by @lefterisgar in https://github.com/sindresorhus/caprine/pull/1942
* Fix new room button shortcut by @lefterisgar in https://github.com/sindresorhus/caprine/pull/1946
* Fix insert buttons (GIF, Sticker, Emoji, Files) shortcuts by @lefterisgar in https://github.com/sindresorhus/caprine/pull/1947
* Fix radio buttons & right sidebar search icon color in dark mode by @lefterisgar in https://github.com/sindresorhus/caprine/pull/1948
* Dark mode fixes by @lefterisgar in https://github.com/sindresorhus/caprine/pull/1955
* Fix new design user menu by @dusansimic in https://github.com/sindresorhus/caprine/pull/1910
* Fix voice message duration text color in dark mode by @dusansimic in https://github.com/sindresorhus/caprine/pull/1959

## New Contributors
* @sfrunza13 made their first contribution in https://github.com/sindresorhus/caprine/pull/1933
* @jrafaelsantana made their first contribution in https://github.com/sindresorhus/caprine/pull/1938

## Dependencies
* Electron bumped to v21 https://github.com/sindresorhus/caprine/commit/04d79e074164ace65d0253283771b567dafe8da7

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/sindresorhus/caprine/compare/v2.56.1...v2.57.0

name: v2.56.1
body:
## Announcement for Linux users
New installation options are available, including automatic updates on Debian-based versions using APT. Check the [readme](https://github.com/sindresorhus/caprine#linux) for more information.

## What's New
* Create new room by @lefterisgar in https://github.com/sindresorhus/caprine/pull/1883

## What's Changed
* Dark mode fixes (top gap, icons, radio buttons' accent color)
* Fix insert buttons (GIF, Sticker, Emoji, Files)
* Fix "Find Conversation" feature
* Fix "Show Message Buttons" option by @lefterisgar and @dusansimic in https://github.com/sindresorhus/caprine/pull/1881
* Fix private mode by @lefterisgar in https://github.com/sindresorhus/caprine/pull/1884
* Remove code related to old design by @lefterisgar in https://github.com/sindresorhus/caprine/pull/1879
* Various improvements to readme by @Danik1601, @dusansimic and @lefterisgar in https://github.com/sindresorhus/caprine/pull/1885

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/sindresorhus/caprine/compare/v2.56.0...v2.56.1

name: v2.56.0
body:
## What's Changed
* Update Electron to 20 by @1nikolas, @nehalvpatel and @lefterisgar
* Update to the new Messenger icon (2020)
* Improved scrollbar theme by @mquevill in #1638
* Add dark mode to cookies notification
* Add maintainers in about dialog by @lefterisgar in https://github.com/sindresorhus/caprine/pull/1874
* Add option to disable automatic updates
* Enable auto-updates on Linux
* Display a notification when a new update is available
* Fix private mode
* Fix adaptive, hidden and narrow sidebar
* Fix "Show Message Buttons" option
* Fix login button color in dark mode
* Fix cookies notification accept button being hidden on smaller windows
* Fix Caprine not starting on some Linux distros
* Fix ci build step by @dusansimic in https://github.com/sindresorhus/caprine/pull/1872
* Fix search icon dark mode color in right sidebar by @dusansimic in https://github.com/sindresorhus/caprine/pull/1849
* Fix shortcuts by @dusansimic in https://github.com/sindresorhus/caprine/pull/1851
* Hide all non-working features
* Hide new Messenger app banner by @1nikolas in https://github.com/lefterisgar/caprine/pull/2
* Select log out as last menu item by @mquevill in https://github.com/sindresorhus/caprine/pull/1853
* Remove "Allow All Cookies" button to increase privacy
* Remove all CSS related to old design

## New Maintainers
* [Lefteris Garyfalakis](https://github.com/lefterisgar)
* [Michael Quevillon](https://github.com/mquevill)
* [Nikolas Spiridakis](https://github.com/1nikolas)
